    <p>"What October 2025 and April 2026 together describe is not a series of bad-actor casinos in an otherwise functional gaming sector. They describe a sector in which the legitimate licensing layer, the casino-property layer, the security-and-staffing layer, and the political-patronage layer were each repurposed at industrial scale for cross-border scam operations."</p>
    <cite>Sanctions compliance specialist tracking the Mekong sub-region, May 2026</cite>
